EXP 1: Create a static webpage using HTML tags and CSS 
<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html> 
<head> 
<title>Here is My Webpage</title> 
<style> 
body{font-family:Arial;text-align:center;background:#d0e7ff;margin:0} 
header,footer{background:#3399ff;color:#fff;padding:10px} 
section{background:#e6f2ff;margin:20px;padding:15px;border-radius:8px} 
</style> 
</head> 
<body> 
<header><h1>Welcome to my portfolio!</h1></header> 
<section><h2>About</h2><p>This is a simple static webpage displaying my 
details.</p></section> 
<footer><p>&copy; 2025 My Webpage</p></footer> 
</body> 
</html> 
